  ('1566b79f-cd79-4ae7-8b8e-3bc0c22d9a36', 'Pilot District Connections to EDU-NET and Simulated Interventions', 'Brianna Moore-Trieu', current_timestamp(),
   'Ready for Review', 'Grant', 'As part of broader System Feedback Loop goals, the investment accelerates time to insights and supports AI-testing of interventions, via simulated planning environments. It also could also serve as a potential pilot for EDU-Net by cooridnating with SafeInsights to enable secure data sharing and interoperability across systems within South San Antionio and other underresourced TX districts,helping validate AI-driven insights and testbeds while addressing interoperability challenges critical to scaling EDU-Net across districts.',
