  ('5c4bb637-1275-4402-a549-ae9715a1389e', 'Data & AI Team Lead Strategy MLE Support', 'Chelsea Koproske', current_timestamp(),
   'Moved to Invest', 'Contract', 'Our ideal partner will work closely with the USP Data & AI team to refine and operationalize the strategy’s results framework and learning agenda, strengthen coherence across portfolios, and embed dynamic measurement and reporting capabilities that ensure our strategy approach remains adaptive and actionable as the education and AI landscape evolves. 
The Strategy Measurement Lead will coordinate across MLE partners, synthesize diverse evidence streams, and model new approaches to using AI to enhance learning and insight generation. 

See full RFP here (linked)',
