  ('d78199f9-a19f-4e1d-90ae-54290652931b', 'Advancing Infrastructure for AI-enabled Assessment', 'Xiaoxue Du', current_timestamp(),
   'Brainstorming', 'Grant', 'The goal of this effort is to convene a minimal viable coalition (MVC) to design, prototype, and pilot AI-enabled evaluation infrastructure for next-generation assessment. This convening focuses on moving from fragmented experimentation toward coordinated system-building — developing concrete infrastructure, testing it in real-world contexts, and generating early evidence to inform broader adoption. This effort is anchored in a shift from static measurement toward systems that reflect how learning actually happens—developmental, contextual, and continuous. At its core, this effort recognizes that advancing next-generation assessment is not primarily a modeling challenge, but an infrastructure challenge—building the system layer that enables longitudinal, multi-modal representations of learner growth and embeds evaluation into continuous learning loops. A critical differentiator is the role of philanthropy in shaping this as a public-good infrastructure: ensuring learner data is owned, portable, and governed by the learner, with transparency, interoperability, and equity by design. Three concrete priorities define the work:
Establish a Learning & Engineering Observatory to support shared experimentation and longitudinal data aggregation across partners.
Embed evaluation directly into learning systems through instrumentation, memory and context integration, and continuous feedback loops.
Enable evaluation to capture multi-modal, longitudinal learning trajectories rather than isolated performance snapshots.',
   'ai-infra', 'ai-infra-bow2', NULL,
   'ASU, Axim', NULL, NULL,
   NULL, NULL, NULL,
   'More details: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1jSqZrdppF4GAc0uyr-UGiSI8uVuzt3eq/edit 

Early stage - this record has already being included in the early entry - we might need to remove this for the duplication', NULL,
   NULL, false, false),
